COVID-19 Status 💉 🦠

As of 7:25AM PT today, over 1.4 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 25.4 thousand have died.

In the last day, 419 new infections were reported and 3 deaths. This is trending downwards.

Fortunately, 22.6 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 12 years and older, 62.4% have their 1st shot and 5.6% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is speeding up, but there are 3.4 million doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~10 days for new deliveries to get into arms. At the current rate, all Canadians aged 12+ should have the first dose by Jul-09 and fully vaccinated by Oct-01. There is no approved vaccine for children aged 11 or younger.
